text: Niscaya allahe tomalokaka bahu ksetrata sahaya karaiche arau huna'inara yud'dhara dina yetiya tomalokaka utphulla karaichila tomalokara sankhyagaraisthata'i, kintu seya tomalokara kono kamata aha nachila arau prthirai prasasta horaa satbe'o tomalokara babe sankirna hai gaichila. Tara pichata tomaloke prstha pradarsana karai palayana karaichila
